&lt;p&gt;Our ideal candidate is a high-agency technical-generalist. Our researchers thrive working autonomously in fast-paced, high-stakes environments. We look for scientists that pair technical excellence with strong ownership of their work. Our researchers feel comfortable guiding the direction of the research alongside our collaborators.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About you&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in ML research, alignment research, or both&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deeply passionate about AI alignment &amp;amp; believe genuine progress is possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent at Python, Pytorch, and the modern deep learning stack&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgeable about building, training, or evaluating deep learning models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable calling AI model APIs via REST or client libraries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adept at decomposing complex problems into concrete, testable experiments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-native, and eager to use AI tools to automate your workflow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrives in a fast-paced, startup-like environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adept in English and comfortable communicating technical work to all audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
