&lt;p&gt;AE Studio is a development, data science, and design studio that works closely with founders and executives to create custom software and machine learning solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We build products, platforms, and internal ventures that increase agency for all conscious beings. We combine world-class software engineering, AI expertise, and product design to ship ambitious projects that matter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Full-Stack Developer&lt;/strong&gt; who bridges modern web engineering with practical AI; someone who can design, build, and ship production-ready, AI-powered applications while maintaining the standards of a top-tier software developer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and ship end-to-end applications from prototype to production across frontend, backend, and cloud.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build clean, scalable APIs and services and integrate AI models where they create real value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create AI pipelines (data ingestion, preprocessing, embeddings, retrieval, orchestration) that are reliable and maintainable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineer prompting strategies and guardrails for real-world performance (latency, cost, accuracy), not just demo hype.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate AI features into full-stack apps with robust APIs, frontend UX, and CI/CD pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with designers, PMs, and engineers to deliver polished product experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously evaluate new AI tools/models for performance, cost, and fit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write production-grade, testable, maintainable code in TypeScript/JavaScript and Python (and other languages as needed).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of professional software engineering experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record shipping production applications (links to live products welcome).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with LLM APIs (e.g., OpenAI, Anthropic), embeddings, vector databases, and orchestration frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong command of modern web stacks (e.g., React/Next.js, Node.js/Nest/Fastify, Python/FastAPI) and cloud infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid grasp of architecture, scalability, performance, and security.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A bias toward shipping with best practices (testing, code reviews, monitoring/observability).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communication, self-management, and comfort in a collaborative remote environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable picking up new languages and frameworks, leveraging modern AI dev tools to move faster.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Sets You Apart&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience fine-tuning models or training custom models on domain-specific data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributions to open-source AI or developer tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mature approach to prompt engineering and evaluation (beyond trial-and-error).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in data engineering or MLOps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for AI alignment, agency-increasing technologies, and ethical AI development.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you can write prompts that work today and code that still works in two years, we want to talk to you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary range from $115k/year to $185k/year (if you&#39;re based in LA). Not in the range? That&#39;s fine, you can still apply and our team may fit you in a more senior position that we&#39;re not actively hiring for right now, since we are growing fast and may have other openings soon.&lt;/p&gt;
