&lt;p&gt;AE Studio is an LA-based company focused on increasing human agency by making the AGI future go well. We believe alignment is solvable, people just haven’t tried hard enough. For us, that means focusing on neglected ideas that could unlock major breakthroughs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’ve spent over a decade helping clients, from startups to companies like Samsung, Walmart, Berkshire Hathaway, and Goodfire, solve complex technical problems and bring ambitious products to life. We apply the same structures to research. Instead of a client, we partner with visionary researchers exploring neglected alignment ideas. We’re a full-stack R&amp;amp;D group combining engineering, science, and product capability. This puts us in a unique position to move quickly and make real progress on one of the most important problems of our time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re fully bootstrapped. We don’t rely on venture capital or private equity. Profits from our client work go directly into internal Skunkworks projects, technical research, and policy engagement. This gives us the freedom to pursue high-risk, high-upside ideas that typical funding models neglect. We can commit to long-term bets without being constrained by short grant cycles or investor timelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our alignment efforts include in-house work, alignment clients like Goodfire AI, and collaborations with Redwood Research and researchers at Anthropic and DeepMind. In the past, we also led pioneering research in brain-computer interfaces, and we continue to expand our scope as the stakes rise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you care about actually solving alignment and want to build, we want to talk to you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring Product Leads. Strategic, AI-fluent technical operators who own delivery for high-stakes projects from end to end and become trusted advisors to senior client stakeholders along the way. This includes client engagements, internal ventures, product-market fit exploration, and enterprise execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hybrid role: part strategic advisor, part technical PM, part AI architect, part founder-in-training. You&#39;ll sit at the table with senior leadership, run complex AI projects across generative AI, automation, agent orchestration, and custom software, build real products, and potentially spin one off. AE supports startup spinouts, so you&#39;ll have the opportunity to become CEO or CTO of a venture, either one we already have in the works or one you help create.&lt;/p&gt;
